%% Flowchart for booking process
flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> AuthCheck{Authenticated?}
    AuthCheck -- No --> Login[Redirect to Login]
    AuthCheck -- Yes --> SelectSlot[Select Slot]
    SelectSlot --> Confirm[Confirm Booking]
    Confirm --> Payment{Payment Required?}
    Payment -- Yes --> Pay[Process Payment]
    Pay --> CreateBooking[Create Booking]
    Payment -- No --> CreateBooking
    CreateBooking --> Notify[Send Confirmation]
    Notify --> End([End])
